## Flowr Cheatsheet

| What | Command | Key fields |
|------|---------|------------|
| Inspect state | `check --session` | `.attrs.owner` `.attrs.skills` `.attrs.in` `.attrs.out` `.transitions` |
| See paths | `next --session` | `.transitions[].status` (`"open"` / `"blocked"`) `.transitions[].conditions` |
| Advance | `transition <trigger> --session` | `.to` (next state) |
| Check condition | `check --session <trigger>` | `.conditions` |
